<center><h1>Afterlife Application</h1></center>
<form method=post action="http://afterlifeguild.org/app.cgi">
<input type="hidden" name="application" value="1">
<center>
<table class="report" width=600 cellpadding=10><tr><td bgcolor="DDDDDD">
<table class="insidereport" border=0>
<tr><td bgcolor="DDDDDD">What is your character's name (first name only)?</td><td bgcolor="DDDDDD"><input type=text name="charname" size=25></td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="DDDDDD">What server do you play on?</td><td bgcolor="DDDDDD"><input type=text name="server" value="Cenarius" size=25></td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="DDDDDD">What is your email address?</td><td bgcolor="DDDDDD"><input type=text name="email" size=25></td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="DDDDDD">Alternate characters (for ease of contact), first names only, space between each name:</td><td bgcolor="DDDDDD"><input type="text" name="alts" size=25></td></tr>
<tr><td bgcolor="DDDDDD" colspan=2 align=center>Class: 
<select name="class">
<option value="Druid">Druid
<option value="Hunter">Hunter
<option value="Mage">Mage
<option value="Paladin">Paladin
<option value="Priest">Priest
<option value="Rogue">Rogue
<option value="Warlock">Warlock
<option value="Warrior">Warrior
</select>
&nbsp; &nbsp;
Level:
<select name="level">
<option value="01">&lt; 60
<option value="60">60
</select>
</td></tr></table>
<p>
Afterlife raid times are 1730 (5:30pm) PST until 2400 (midnight) PST, every day.  While we don't regularly raid this much, the potential is there.  What times can you raid?  What time zone are you located in?
<p><center><textarea name="answer1" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Do you meet our entrance requirements (entrance requirements can be found at ( http://www.afterlifeguild.org/template.cgi?page=joining )?  If not, why?
<p><center><textarea name="answer2" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Provide a link to a profile of your current gear. Allakhazam's, Thottbot, CTProfiles, etc. Having raid ready gear will signifigantly increase your chances.
<p><center><textarea name="answer3" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Has an Afterlife member agreed to sponsor you, if so, who?  Who else do you know from Afterlife and how?
<p><center><textarea name="answer4" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>


Why do you want to join Afterlife? Tell us more about your reasons for applying.
<p><center><textarea name="answer5" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Successful raiding is as much about preparation as it is about execution.  When you're not raiding, what are you doing to prepare for challenging raids?"
<p><center><textarea name="answer6" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

How well do you know your class?  Briefly explain your answer.
<p><center><textarea name="answer7" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

What raiding have you done?
<p><center><textarea name="answer8" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

How well do you know your class role in a raid situation?  Briefly explain your answer.
<p><center><textarea name="answer9" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

What do you think you can bring to Afterlife?  And, why do you think your style of play will work well with our guild?
<p><center><textarea name="answer10" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

List all previous online guilds you have belonged to. Why did you leave them?
<p><center><textarea name="answer11" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>

Parting Comments? (optional)
<p><center><textarea name="answer12" cols=60 rows=10></textarea></center><p>
<p>
<b>Double check the above before submitting.  There is no <i>are you sure?</i> page, and corrupt applications are disarded without notice.</b><p>
</td></tr></table>
<input type=submit value="Submit Application">
</center>
</form>
